<div class="news-item">
    <p class="news-item-title">Scab Forum Presentation</p>
    <p class="news-item-date">Dec 5, 2022</p>
    <div class="news-item-content">
        <p>The presentation of T3/Breedbase given at the 2022 Wheat &amp; Barley Scab Forum can be found 
        <a href="/static_content/files/2022ScabForum.pdf">here</a>.  It includes information about the main features 
        of T3/Breedbase, a general overview of creating phenotype upload templates, and highlights some of T3/Breedbase's 
        advanced features (such as Seedlots and Barcodes).</p>
    </div>
</div>

