<div class="news-item">
    <p class="news-item-title">Speaking of Oats...</p>
    <p class="news-item-date">February 26, 2020</p>
    <div class="news-item-content">
        <p>
            T3 gave the January <a href="https://oatnews.org/node/921">Speaking of Oats</a> webinar organized by 
            <a href="https://oatglobal.umn.edu/">Oat Global</a> and <a href="https://oatnews.org/">the Oat Newsletter</a>, 
            where we discussed practical applications of T3/Breedbase for the oat community and an overview of adding and 
            extracting data from the new database.
        </p>
        <p>
            A <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NFoytBWj29Q">video recording of the webinar</a> is now available on YouTube and 
            a <a href="https://oatnews.org/oatnews_pdfs/2020/SOO_QA_21Jan2021.pdf">transcript of the Q&A session (PDF)</a> is available 
            from the Oat Newsletter.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="news-item">
    <p class="news-item-title">Breedbase Workshop Notes &amp; Videos</p>
    <p class="news-item-date">September 10, 2020</p>
    <div class="news-item-content">
        <p>
            T3 hosted a practical remote workshop demonstrating the process of uploading field trial data to the database.
            Notes from that workshop, which include step-by-step instructions on how to upload a sample dataset, are 
            <a href="/static_content/files/2020ScabWorkshop/notes.html">now available</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Video recordings of the workshop are available on the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3jrvvzGKKEHzOriDBgnj0A/videos">
            Breedbase YouTube Channel</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

